Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.85,0:18:32.75,Mofurun_CN,,0,0,0,,mofu !
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.07,0:18:38.97,MagiMiraJP,,0,0,0,,{\fs50\b1}ルビー！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.07,0:18:38.97,Curerpp_ML,,0,0,0,,Ruby !
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.07,0:18:38.97,MagiMiraCN,,0,0,0,,{\fs50\b1}红宝石！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.47,0:18:43.32,MagiMiraJP,,0,0,0,,紅の情熱よ 私達の手に！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.47,0:18:43.32,MagiMiraCN,,0,0,0,,赤色的激情 燃烧于我等之手！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.30,0:18:49.87,MagiMiraJP,,0,0,0,,{\fs50\b1}フル フル リンクル！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.30,0:18:49.87,Curerpp_ML,,0,0,0,,Full Full Linkru !
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.30,0:18:49.87,MagiMiraCN,,0,0,0,,{\fs50\b1}心有灵犀 将你与我 紧密相连！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.44,0:19:04.37,MagiMiraJP,,0,0,0,,{\fs50\b1}プリキュア ルビーパッショナーレ！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.44,0:19:04.37,Curerpp_ML,,0,0,0,,Precure Ruby Passionale !
